+                    footprint on our infrastructure. We try to use
+                    privacy-friendly open source software and privacy-friendly
+                    third parties as much as possible.
+                  </p>
+                  <p>
+                    This document outlines our responsibilities and duties
+                    regarding the processing of your personal data, as defined
+                    by Art. 13 of the European Union's General Data Protection
